content: A lady asked me to pass her name through our organization for a project she's working with climate change. Is that possible?

Hi Madeline! We don't want to collect any voter information for their security. We also aren't able to promote non-campaign events on Discord. If she wants to connect to the campaign directing her to kamalaharris.com is the best.
Hi Erica thanks for letting me know! I ended the call with her but next time in the future if someone is interested I'll direct them to kamalaharris.com.
<@415244010928472074> We also have a climate engagement team here on Discord, so you can invite ppl to join our office and connect with other likeminded vols
Gotcha, thank you Jen! How can they join the office?

WHAT IS THE INVITE TO THIS SERVER?

https://discord.gg/teamharris
